OL,3,CPM 'talking to chief constable about
OL,4,Cpossible' PSNI support
OL,6,FThe Prime Minister has not ruled out
OL,7,Fmaking more money available to the
OL,8,FPSNI following the summer's unrest.
OL,10,FHe was responding to a question from
OL,11,FDUP Leader Gavin Robinson in the House
OL,12,Fof Commons.
OL,14,FSir Keir Starmer said it was important
OL,15,Fthat he met with injured officers
OL,16,Fduring a recent visit to Northern
OL,17,FIreland.
