OL,3,CPM 'talking to chief constable about
OL,4,Cpossible' PSNI support
OL,6,F"I do recognise the difficult
OL,7,Ffinancial position the PSNI faces, and
OL,8,Fthe chief constable and I have spoken
OL,9,Fabout this on more than one occasion,"
OL,10,Fthe Prime Minister said.
OL,12,F"Predominantly it's for the justice
OL,13,Fminister and the Executive to set the
OL,14,FPSNI's budget and an operational
OL,15,Fmatter for the chief constable on how
OL,16,Fhe allocates that, but I have been
OL,17,Ftalking to him about what further
OL,18,Fsupport might be possible."
