OL,3,CPM 'talking to chief constable about
OL,4,Cpossible' PSNI support
OL,6,FMr Robinson said the "chronic
OL,7,Funderfunding of policing and public
OL,8,Fservices" in Northern Ireland needs to
OL,9,Fbe addressed.
OL,11,F"Northern Ireland needs effective
OL,12,Fpolicing to ensure community safety
OL,13,Fand combat crime in all its forms," he
OL,14,Fsaid.
OL,16,F"However, we are seeing growing
OL,17,Fpressures on neighbourhood policing,
OL,18,Fcrime investigations, and PSNI
OL,19,Fofficers.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/5
