OL,3,CPM 'talking to chief constable about
OL,4,Cpossible' PSNI support
OL,6,F"It is also crucial that the PSNI has
OL,7,Fthe necessary resources to combat the
OL,8,Fongoing threat from dissident
OL,9,Frepublicans who still seek to unleash
OL,10,Fterror in our community.
OL,12,F"The chronic underfunding of policing
OL,13,Fand public services in Northern
OL,14,FIreland must be addressed. We will
OL,15,Fcontinue to press the Government to
OL,16,Ftackle these challenges and urge
OL,17,Fothers to support, not undermine, this
OL,18,Fcrucial message."
